The missile launcher component of the Mobile Air Defense system. It must be connected to a dedicated radar unit to find and track targets (not necessarily the MAD-4 radar). It can only move while Engage Enemies is unchecked (launch tubes will fold). The MAD-4 system features super long range radar and missile technology on a mobile platform.

The radar component of the Mobile Air Defense system. It can only move while Engage Enemies is unchecked (radar components will fold). The MAD-4 system features super long range radar and missile technology on a mobile platform.
